'From Squeak2.9alpha of 12 June 2000 [latest update: #2867] on 14 October 2000 at 11:20:02 pm'!"Change Set:		ThreeEventFixesDate:			14 October 2000Author:			Dan IngallsFixes three bugs remaining from the overhaul of HandMorph:	MoviePlayerMorph menu commands don't work	Can't type into CypherPanel	Scrolling seems to get into weird states if you use the elevator"!!MoviePlayerMorph methodsFor: 'menu' stamp: 'di 10/14/2000 23:15'!invokeBookMenu	"Invoke the book's control panel menu."	| aMenu |	aMenu _ MVCMenuMorph new defaultTarget: self.	aMenu addList:	#(			('make thumbnail'		thumbnailForThisPage)			('open movie file'		openMovieFile)			('add sound track'		addSoundTrack)		).	aMenu popUpEvent: self world activeHand lastEvent in: self world! !!WordGameLetterMorph methodsFor: 'typing' stamp: 'di 10/14/2000 22:36'!handlesKeyboard: evt	^ true! !"Postscript:Update extant scrollbars:"ScrollBar allSubInstancesDo: [:sb | sb initializeSlider].!